definitions.text:
@bì bọp
- Flop, plop
=sóng vỗ bì bọp vào mạn thuyền+the waves struck flop, flop against the sides of the boat

@bì bõm
- With a plashing noise, plashingly
=lội bì bõm qua thửa ruộng lầy+to wade through the marshy field with a plashing noise, to splash through the marshy field

@bì sì
* adj
- Taciturn, of few words

@bì bạch
- With a smack
=vỗ bụng bì bạch+to slap one's belly with a smack
